UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText` = 'Captain Vimes thinks the Grimtotems are behind the destruction of the Shady Rest Inn? They wouldn''t have been first on my list of suspects, but if Captain Vimes sent you here to follow up on a lead, he must have his reasons. Regardless, the Grimtotems have been a thorn in our side for some time and we''re always glad to have the extra help.' WHERE `entry` = 11143;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `Details` = 'You''ve done some good work, $n, best I''ve seen from an amateur.$b$bLady Proudmoore asked that I keep her apprised of this delicate situation, and I haven''t spoken to her for some time now.$b$bI was going to deliver my report to her later, but it seems more fitting that you should be the one to speak with her about it. You can probably answer her questions better than I could.', `OfferRewardText` = '' WHERE `entry` = 1288;
